{"tid":1381434,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"成立獨立調查委員會有感","createTime":"2019-07-29T08:36:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T09:37:39.000Z","uid":189799,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0abe55e788a61cef4117eda1c1417a70ce7d0906","tid":1381434,"uid":189799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T08:36:28.000Z","msg":"近日，多左post反對成立委員會。<br />\n<br />\n反對嘅主要因為<br />\n1.唔夠公正，咩都查唔到<br />\n2.運動會因此完結，雙普選先係有用<br />\n<br />\n其實關鍵係委員會係咪真係可以查到野呢。若果查到警黑勾結，政府錯失，其實對爭取雙普選係有幫助。<br />\n<br />\n7警案其實主要係因為TVB無作供而判輕。<br />\n我宜家仲信法官係相對公正。<br />\n就算今次唔搵立場較開明嘅人做主席，只要一啲相對中立嘅法官就得。因為今次運動1個月咁耐，黑警可以話係錯漏百出，以721為例，我諗唔到有咩藉口幫佢地開脫。<br />\n而且，林鄭咁驚委員會，某程度上，顯示委員會係有佢嘅威力。<br />\n雙普選係長期目標，爭取到固然好，但若果運動持續唔到咁耐，先成立獨立調查委員會係咪較可行呢?而委員會亦可能係日後爭取雙普選嘅力量。"},{"pid":"125bf8efd7dc9f4db47600ebe0db065a4b282f23","tid":1381434,"uid":263161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T08:38:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"da599026b3ee383e2abfcb413d146c61871e9e5f","tid":1381434,"uid":229019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T09:05:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WMV3tnr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWMV3tnr.png&h=77fc1786&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9Rgez2q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9Rgez2q.png&h=b86a56fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LgkSmHq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLgkSmHq.jpg&h=d447c2f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KY6Vjt5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKY6Vjt5.jpg&h=18989aa7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pLe7U2r.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpLe7U2r.jpg&h=98c959ff&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ed5ff260f03ce9fb15b72819bb51294508a8d49b","tid":1381434,"uid":189799,"like":0,"dislike":